      </li>
      <li id="fn-h">
        h — Commission ranges are directional; no OTA publishes a rate card. The firmest anchor is
        Booking Holdings’ FY2024 blended take rate of ~14.3% (revenue ÷ gross bookings). Cancellation
        by channel: D-EDGE, October 2024 — direct 11.1%, Booking.com group 42% (Europe). Channel mix:
