        route.
      </li>
      <li id="fn-l">
        l — Champions 12.3 (WRI/WRAP-backed), <em>The Business Case for Reducing Food Loss and Waste:
        Hotels</em>, 2018 — 21% average kitchen food-waste reduction in year one across 42 hotel sites
        in 15 countries; $7 saved per $1 invested. The strongest non-vendor evidence in the category.
      </li>
      <li id="fn-m">
